text: Emmendingen is a rural district (Landkreis) in the west of Baden-Württemberg, Germany. Neighboring districts are Ortenaukreis, Schwarzwald-Baar, Breisgau- Hochschwarzwald and the district-free city Freiburg. To the west, it borders the French department Bas-Rhin.
